headline: Samsara Inc. (IOT) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Samsara Inc. (IOT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 75% and 3.65%, respectively, for the quarter ended October 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
